<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <title>Cadastrar Dados</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main
      class="min-h-svh flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-stone-100"
    >
      <section class="max-w-100 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Concluir Cadastro</h1>
          <p class="text-stone-700">
            Preencha o formulário abaixo para concluir o seu cadastro.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          role="alert"
          class="text-sm p-4 border border-blue-400 bg-blue-50 rounded-md flex items-start gap-1.5"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="lucide lucide-lock-keyhole-icon lucide-lock-keyhole shrink-0 size-4.5 mt-0.5"
          >
            <circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1" />
            <rect x="3" y="10" width="18" height="12" rx="2" />
            <path d="M7 10V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3" />
          </svg>
          <p>Suas credenciais serão criptografadas no nosso banco de dados.</p>
        </div>

        <form method="post" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <input type="hidden" name="plataforma" value="{{.Plataforma}}" />
          <input type="hidden" name="plataforma_id" value="{{.PlataformaID}}" />
          <div class="grid gap-1">
            <label for="sei_usuario">Usuário do SEI</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="sei_usuario"
              id="sei_usuario"
              required
              class="p-2 rounded border border-stone-200"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-1">
            <label for="sei_senha">Senha do SEI</label>
            <input
              type="password"
              name="sei_senha"
              id="sei_senha"
              required
              class="p-2 rounded border border-stone-200"
            />
          </div>
          <button
            class="px-4 py-2 rounded bg-stone-900 text-white font-semibold"
          >
            Enviar
          </button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
